text: Regina Elphinstone is a former provincial electoral division in the Canadian province of Saskatchewan. It was the riding of former Premier Allan Blakeney and later of former Deputy Premier Dwain Lingenfelter. ==Members of the Legislative Assembly== {| border=1 cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 |- bgcolor="EEEEEE" !
